Description: Get ready for a fun underwater journey. Move through the submarine full of obstacles. Guide the shark character. Buy characters with the gold you will earn at the end of the game and experience the excitement. You can explore the submarine in 15 different levels or endless mode. Destroy 3 different boss characters and dominate the submarine! For more, try Super Shark World now!
Instructions: Move = "W,A,S,D" or "Arrow Keys", Shoot = "K", Dash = "L"

Title: Wrestler Rush
Description: Dodge your rivals and smack down. Be aware of obstacles or you cannot reach to the ring! Swipe your character and avoid obstacles. Show your strength at the end!
Instructions: Use left moue button to strafe your character.

Title: Virus Ninja 2
Description: Dangerous virus strains are spreading everywhere again. You, a ninja master, have come back to slice them out and protect people. PLAY NOW!
Instructions: Swiping by mouse or finger to slice the viruses.

Title: Guess Animal Names
Description: "Welcome to 'Guess Animal Name'! Challenge your animal knowledge by identifying the pictured animal and completing its spelling. Simply click on the needed alphabet letters, but be cautious; a wrong click costs a life out of five. Ready to test your animal expertise?"
Instructions: Use mouse or touch pad to select the alphabet letter.

Title: Silly Ways To Die 2
Description: These crazy creatures can't stop hurting themselves. Can you help protect them before it's too late?
Instructions: Use your mouse and your quick reactions to prevent yourself from dying.

Title: Queen Clara Then and Now
Description: Clara is a beautiful queen for the wonderland, She likes to wear her traditional wear and modern wear today. Can you help her to make her more beautiful by choosing the best outfits for both styles? Let's check her beauty then and now. Have great fun!
Instructions: Use mouse only

Title: Over Rooftops
Description: Run as fast as you can and don't stop jumping over rooftops, collect maximum amount of fish falling from the plane, be careful not to fall or get hit by the western creatures that roam the rooftops at night, meow at the western creatures to eliminate them.
Instructions:
[Right arrow] Increase running speed
[Left arrow] Decrease running speed
[up arrow] Jump up
[X button] Attack

Title: Tank Shootout
Description: Tank shootout is an interesting skill based shooting game. Destroy all the targets to complete a level. Use mouse or touch input, to set the speed and direction of bullet to chase the target successfully.  You will get limited number of bullets for each level so use them wisely to win it. You can take the help of power panel to see the current power and last shot’s power. Mini map shows the position of target, the location where the previous shot reached etc.
Instructions: Use mouse or touchscreen to play this game.

Title: Spartan Mahjong
Description: Simplified classic Mahjong game with Spartan theme. You can eliminate pair of similar items. You can select only those pairs which have either left or right side open. Hints can help you. Try out the classic Mahjong game. Make connections between the matching tiles while you fight to keep up with the clock. Can you clear the board before time runs out? Unused hints and saved time will be awarded as bonus.
Instructions: Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.

Title: 2048 Runner
Description:
Navigate through a series of gates and cubes, avoid the negative gates and go in the positive ones and merge to the same cube, but avoid the cubes with different number, you can't merge with them.
You must arrive at the end of level with a number that is greater than or equal to the level's objective.
With fast reflexes and strategic thinking, you must outwit the negative gates and keep their number from reaching zero in order to make it through each level and ultimately win the game.
Instructions: Hold left mouse button and swipe left or right to move

Title: PAUSED
Description:
Time only works for one of us!

You mission is to help the duckling and his bunny friend reach the end by manipulating time.
Instructions:
Move    - A, D, Left Arrow, and Right Arrow
Jump    - W, Z,  B, or Up Arrow
Fall       - S or Down Arrow
Switch - X, N, Space, or Enter
Reload - R
Pause   - Escape or P
Key Features:
- Short and fun experience.
- Around 19 levels.
- Beautiful minimal graphics.
- Easy puzzles.
- Two characters with two different abilities.
- You control time, sort of!

Title: Touchdrawn
Description: Draw offensive lines so that the football player can win the game successfully. Don't get the ball by the opponent. When necessary, your teammates will come back to help you.
Instructions: Tap to play.
